<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_06_IH_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema614_05_ih_0003.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema614_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ena614_06">
      <section class="title type2 star_title">
        <h2 data-head="5" lang="y" class="is_star">
          <span lang="y"
            >주차장에 있는 자동차 20대 중 전기차는 7대입니다. 전기차 수는 전체 자동차 수의 몇 ％인지 이준이와 시은이의 방법으로 각각 <br />
            나타내어 보세요.</span
          >
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents p_bottom">
        <div class="ema_614_06_0005">
          <div class="box">
            <span class="name"> 이준 </span>
            <div class="txt">
              <p>
                기준량을 100으로 할 때의<br />
                비율로 바꾸어 나타내 봐.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_in">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box flex">
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>=</p>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>35</span>
                    <span>100</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>=35 ％</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex justify_center bottom gap_4">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="35"></math-field>
                </div>
                <p class="ml_5">％</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="box">
            <span class="name"> 시은 </span>
            <div class="txt">
              <p>
                비율에 100을 곱해서 나온<br />
                값에 ％를 붙여 나타내 봐.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_in">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box flex">
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>×100=35</p>
                  <span class="arrow"></span>
                  <p>35 ％</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex justify_center bottom gap_4">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="35"></math-field>
                </div>
                <p class="ml_5">％</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div class="flex gap_4 align_center">
                  <label class="jun">이준이의 방법</label>
                  <p>전체 자동차 수에 대한 전기차 수의 비율은</p>
                  <div class="fraction_box ml_5">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>이므로 기준량을 100으로 바꾸면</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap_4 align_center">
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>=</p>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>35</span>
                    <span>100</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>=35 ％입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap_4 align_center">
                  <label class="sen">시은이의 방법</label>
                  <p>전체 자동차 수에 대한 전기차 수의 비율은</p>
                  <div class="fraction_box ml_5">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>이므로 비율에 100을 곱하면</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap_4 align_center">
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <p>×100=35</p>
                  <p>➔</p>
                  <p>35 ％입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
